             was indicted for <rs id="t18310512-133-off786" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18310512-133-off786" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18310512-133-off786" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18310512-133-cd787" type="crimeDate">22nd of April</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310512-133-off786 t18310512-133-cd787"></join>, 2 rings, value 6s.; 1 pair of earrings, value 6s.; 1 handkerchief, value 4s.; 1 half-crown, 1 shilling, and 1 sixpence, the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18310512-133-victim1012" type="victimName">
                           Mary 
                           Beney
                        <interp inst="t18310512-133-victim1012" type="surname" value="Beney"></interp>
